OL,5, An ex-Wales footballer has described   
OL,6, being asked to remove her "rainbow     
OL,7, wall" bucket hat as she entered a World
OL,8, Cup stadium in Qatar.                  
OL,10,FLaura McAllister, a gay woman and past 
OL,11,FFifa Council candidate, said she was   
OL,12,Ftold to remove her hat before the start
OL,13,Fof Wales' opener against the USA.      
OL,15,FThe rainbow version of Welsh fan hats  
OL,16,Fshows support for the LGBTQ+ community.
OL,18,FFifa - world football's governing body,
OL,19,Fwhich is responsible for the tournament
OL,20,F- has been asked to comment.           
